{"title":"口外民谣","authors":["浴岩"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"口外民谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤二虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浴岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤二虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白眼狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在省政府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光会要钱粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本进了热河境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向南退却跑的慌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一退退到了长城里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎民百姓泪汪汪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰对苍天高声骂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤二虎没有人心肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党那管百姓苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当官就为征草粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二虎大肚坠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓饿断肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年大旱浇黄土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后只落两把糠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少百姓死路旁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）汤二虎是国民党热河省主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条大路长又长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮车轮儿滚滚转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛇骡铜铃响叮当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千车粮食千车布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千车募来的棉衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问车儿要到那儿去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口外百姓有饥荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里鹅毛礼义重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表表解放区百姓好心肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万水千山路途远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯兄弟心一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你若问这是谁的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席朱总司令好主张。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}